msgid "Keyboard layout: {layout}"
msgstr ""

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:821
msgid ""
"Auto-selected from your language. Override if your physical keyboard differs."
msgstr ""

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:961
msgid "Welcome to Universal-Lite"
msgstr "Universal-Lite에 오신 것을 환영합니다"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:967
msgid "Create your account to get started."
msgstr "계정을 만들어 시작하세요."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:975
msgid "Jane Doe"
msgstr "홍길동"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1007
msgid "Administrator account (sudo)"
msgstr "관리자 계정 (sudo)"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1040
msgid "Connect to Wi-Fi"
msgstr "Wi-Fi 연결"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1046
msgid "Select a network to get online."
msgstr "네트워크를 선택하여 인터넷에 연결하세요."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1060
#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1573
msgid "Scanning for networks..."
msgstr "네트워크 검색 중..."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1068
msgid "Rescan"
msgstr "재검색"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1094
#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1677
#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1683
msgid "Connect"
msgstr "연결"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1105
msgid "Join hidden network..."
msgstr "숨겨진 네트워크에 연결..."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1141
msgid "Choose Installation Disk"
msgstr "설치 디스크 선택"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1147
msgid "Select the target drive and installation options."
msgstr "대상 드라이브와 설치 옵션을 선택하세요."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1158
#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2200
msgid "Unknown"
msgstr "알 수 없음"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1166
#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1872
msgid "No eligible drives found"
msgstr "사용 가능한 드라이브를 찾을 수 없습니다"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1209
msgid ""
"zswap uses compressed RAM as a cache and spills to a disk swap file when "
"full."
msgstr ""
"zswap은 압축된 메모리를 캐시로 사용하며, 가득 차면 디스크의 스왑 파일로 넘깁"
"니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1226
msgid "All data on the selected drive will be erased."
msgstr "선택한 드라이브의 모든 데이터가 삭제됩니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1249
msgid "System Setup"
msgstr "시스템 설정"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1292
msgid "Your computer's name on the network. Leave blank to auto-generate."
msgstr ""

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1318
msgid "Install Apps"
msgstr "앱 설치"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1325
msgid ""
"These apps are pre-downloaded and will be copied during install. Uncheck any "
"you don't want."
msgstr ""
"이 앱들은 미리 다운로드되어 있으며 설치 중에 복사됩니다. 원하지 않는 앱은 선"
"택을 해제하세요."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1382
msgid "Ready to Install"
msgstr "설치 준비 완료"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1388
msgid "Review your settings and click Install to begin."
msgstr "설정을 확인한 후 '설치'를 클릭하여 시작하세요."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1425
msgid "Installing..."
msgstr "설치 중..."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1437
#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1467
msgid "Show details ▼"
msgstr "세부 정보 표시 ▼"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1467
msgid "Hide details ▲"
msgstr "세부 정보 숨기기 ▲"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1486
msgid "Skip"
msgstr "건너뛰기"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1493
msgid "Retry"
msgstr "재시도"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1500
msgid "Reboot"
msgstr "재부팅"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1613
msgid "No networks found."
msgstr "네트워크를 찾을 수 없습니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1640
msgid "Strong"
msgstr "강함"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1642
msgid "Medium"
msgstr "보통"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1644
msgid "Weak"
msgstr "약함"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1650
msgid "WPA3"
msgstr ""

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1652
msgid "Secured"
msgstr "보안됨"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1654
msgid "Open"
msgstr "열림"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1674
msgid "Password"
msgstr "비밀번호"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1708
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Connecting to {ssid}..."
msgstr "{ssid}에 연결 중..."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1773
#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1796
msgid "Wrong password."
msgstr "비밀번호가 틀렸습니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1775
#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1798
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Connection failed: {err}"
msgstr "연결 실패: {err}"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1783
msgid "Enter a network name."
msgstr "네트워크 이름을 입력하세요."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1811
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Connected to {ssid}!"
msgstr "{ssid}에 연결되었습니다!"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1816
msgid "Connected, but no internet access detected."
msgstr "연결되었지만 인터넷 접속이 감지되지 않았습니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1937
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Step {n} of {total}"
msgstr "{total}단계 중 {n}단계"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1946
msgid "Install"
msgstr "설치"

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1972
msgid "No target drives found. Connect a drive and restart the installer."
msgstr ""
"대상 드라이브를 찾을 수 없습니다. 드라이브를 연결하고 설치 프로그램을 다시 시"
"작하세요."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:1977
msgid "Custom swap size must be a positive whole number (in GB)."
msgstr "사용자 지정 스왑 크기는 양의 정수여야 합니다(단위: GB)."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2000
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Swap size ({swap} GB) is too large for this drive. Maximum recommended: "
"{max} GB."
msgstr ""

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2029
msgid "Full name is required."
msgstr "이름을 입력해야 합니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2032
msgid "Username is required."
msgstr "사용자 이름을 입력해야 합니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2035
msgid "Username must be 32 characters or fewer."
msgstr "사용자 이름은 32자 이하여야 합니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2039
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Username must start with a lowercase letter or underscore, contain only "
"lowercase letters, numbers, underscores, and hyphens, and cannot end with a "
"hyphen."
msgstr ""
"사용자 이름은 소문자로 시작해야 하며, 소문자, 숫자, 하이픈만 사용할 수 있습니"
"다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2045
msgid "Password is required."
msgstr "비밀번호를 입력해야 합니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2048
msgid "Password must be at least 6 characters."
msgstr ""

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2051
msgid "Passwords do not match."
msgstr "비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2057
msgid ""
"Either enable administrator access or set a root password. Without one of "
"these you will be locked out of system management."
msgstr ""
"관리자 접근을 활성화하거나 root 비밀번호를 설정하세요. 둘 다 설정하지 않으면 "
"시스템 관리가 불가능해집니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2067
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hostname must be 63 characters or fewer."
msgstr "사용자 이름은 32자 이하여야 합니다."

#: files/usr/bin/universal-lite-setup-wizard:2071
msgid ""
"Hostname must contain only letters, numbers, and hyphens, and cannot start "
"or end with a hyphen."
msgstr ""

